Display thumbnail preview
Show uploaded timestamp
Update document counter
Status changes to: Uploaded - Pending Review
Upload Card After Success:

📄 Aadhaar Front  [✅]
✅ Uploaded - Pending Review
Uploaded: 26-Jul 10:45 AM
[View] [Replace]


Actions Available:
